在火星车沿途地表以下10至35米深度范围内识别出76个地下倾斜反射体。这些发射体空间分布广泛且均匀，覆盖范围超过1.3千米，所有反射体均呈现向北方低地方向倾斜的特征，倾角介于6°至20°之间、平均倾角为14.5°，且在相同位置的不同深度可观测到多个平行分布的反射体。这些层理结构与地球沿海沉积物的雷达成像结果十分相似，其一致性和物理特性排除了风成沙堆、熔岩管道或河流冲积等其他成因。这些沉积物的大规模存在表明，风浪驱动的沿岸输送为海岸线提供了稳定的泥沙净流入，并形成了海岸线前积层，这种结构只有在持久稳定的大型水体环境中才能形成，而非仅仅是局部和短暂的融水现象。 更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"},"attached_info":"CkIIsZqP38zOp7U4EAMaCTExMzY5OTY3OCCAwIS+BjAAOOMDQARyCzEzNjIxMzM3MjcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"150 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e6496b76fd0fe1dda23a8e89e9824f18_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1740877290.718729","card_id":"Q_13619041106","target":{"id":13619041106,"title":"小米su7 ultra原本准备卖80多万的车，为什么能降到52.99万？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/13619041106","type":"question","created":1740708601,"answer_count":681,"follower_count":1354,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"是亏本卖，还是哪些方面的成本降低了？"},"attached_info":"CkIIsZqP38zOp7U4EAMaCTExMzY5OTIzMCD5tYS+BjAAOMoKQAVyCzEzNjE5MDQxMTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"140 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-ee3fd8060849e177c4a0d3acf0cf1214_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1740877290.718958","card_id":"Q_13799166723","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":13799166723,"title":"英国与乌克兰签署 22.6 亿英镑贷款协议，以加强乌国防能力，释放了哪些信号？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/13799166723","type":"question","created":1740870791,"answer_count":65,"follower_count":101,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline